{"tid":1053094,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去親旅行 天氣都唔好","createTime":"2019-03-08T18:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T18:48:11.000Z","uid":215732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dee517df67f6616d681c9e1c9a61bcfd94203e78","tid":1053094,"uid":215732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T18:26:19.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪我有魔咒<br />\n每次去親旅行個天緊係唔靚<br />\n天公不做美<br />\n每次去完都帶住遺憾咁走<br />\n見唔到最靚果一面<br />\n搞到成日都心私私好想再去<br />\n唔講咁多 去圖<br />\n<br />\n呢張明明係天空之鏡 但成天都係雲 屌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziOoH4w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziOoH4w.png&h=40e301d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03ee32379792fe852e6e57fc84059f0c48aa51d6","tid":1053094,"uid":215732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T18:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iwgxBrm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwgxBrm.png&h=daf009e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又係成個天都係雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59721103e48934bb9d4f90a7834094295adf8ba","tid":1053094,"uid":215732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T18:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qLyDwZT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqLyDwZT.png&h=8583bf98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張左手邊果座係珠穆朗瑪峰黎<br />\n屌 有雲 結果連個山峰頂都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a75e06fa5c13278b73fca99c45743e3954545f","tid":1053094,"uid":19095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T18:33:35.000Z","msg":"雨神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係古代一定好受歡迎"},{"pid":"8af4f109482c5a47ccdc02fab8467cdc9f090529","tid":1053094,"uid":215732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d2a75e06fa5c13278b73fca99c45743e3954545f","tid":1053094,"uid":19095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re